      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Loss = CP-SP = 800-680 = 120\nStep 2: L% = (120/800) x 100 = 15%\n\n  CP |████████████████████| 100%\n  SP |█████████████████   |  85%\n\nTRICK:\n120/800 = 3/20 = 15%\nOr: SP/CP = 680/800 = 0.85 → 15% loss\n\nAnswer: Loss = 15% ✓",
