      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Charges for 1000g, gives 900g\nStep 2: Extra = 1000-900 = 100g\nStep 3: Gain% = (100/900) x 100 = 11.11%\n\nTRICK:\nFormula: (True-False)/False x 100\n= (1000-900)/900 x 100 = 11.11%\nBase is always FALSE weight!\n\nAnswer: Gain = 11.11% ✓",
