      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Let CP per item = 1\n  CP of 20 = 20, SP of 16 = 20\nStep 2: SP per item = 20/16 = 1.25\nStep 3: P% = 0.25/1 x 100 = 25%\n\nTRICK:\nP% = (X-Y)/Y x 100\n= (20-16)/16 x 100 = 25%\nX>Y=Profit, X<Y=Loss\n\nAnswer: Profit = 25% ✓",
