    {
      "id": "el_55",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1602,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Pays for 3, Gets 4 items\nStep 2: Saves 1 out of 4 items\nStep 3: D% = (1/4) x 100 = 25%\n\n  Pays: |===|===|===|   | 3\n  Gets: |===|===|===|===| 4\n\nTRICK:\nD% = Free/(Buy+Free) x 100\n= 1/4 x 100 = 25%\nTRAP: NOT 1/3=33%!\n\nAnswer: Effective discount = 25% ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
