      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Pays for 3, Gets 4 items\nStep 2: Saves 1 out of 4 items\nStep 3: D% = (1/4) x 100 = 25%\n\n  Pays: |===|===|===|   | 3\n  Gets: |===|===|===|===| 4\n\nTRICK:\nD% = Free/(Buy+Free) x 100\n= 1/4 x 100 = 25%\nTRAP: NOT 1/3=33%!\n\nAnswer: Effective discount = 25% ✓",
