    {
      "id": "el_65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1972,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A→B: 1000x120/100 = 1200\nStep 2: B→C: 1200x90/100 = 1080\n\n  1000 --+20%--> 1200 --10%--> 1080\n\nTRICK:\nNet% = P-L-(PxL)/100\n= 20-10-200/100 = +8%\nC = 1000 x 108/100 = Rs.1080\n\nAnswer: C's price = Rs.1080 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
