      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1907,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A manufacturer's cost price is Rs.1000. The goods are sold\nthrough a chain at 10%, 20%, and 25% profit margins\nrespectively. What does the customer pay?",
